66
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:15,690
Myslím, že jsi myslela give and take.

67
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:18,420
Ty hlupačko.

68
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:26,130
Give and take...

69
00:06:27,170 --> 00:06:28,530
out!

70
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,040
